=Description=

"This paper draws attention to the potential cause of " the [[Tragedy of the Commons]] " , which locks people into economic systems that compel the pursuit of self-interest and eventually bring ruin to all. The potential cause consists in numerous issues of money and money equivalents that defy the first and the second law of thermodynamics under the legal arrangement."

